<plot>Joshua, a struggling filmmaker, has just received his big break - a sweet deal with a major studio to direct a film he wrote. Just as it can't get any better, a twist of fate invites a different ending to his story... "Harmonica Swing" is a story about coming to terms with one's faults and limitations, being open to criticism, and even words of wisdom from the entirely unexpected people.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?230657</url></doc>
